														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2130338">
									

<p>&#8230;this was the most uncomfortable tale I've ever read. It's about SCP-231, and it looked like something horrible was going to happen because Montauk, and I was about ready to downvote it.</p>
<p>And then I saw what you did. You Son of a Gunpei Yokoi, creator of the Game Boy. Scared the <em>crap</em> outta me.</p>
<p>+1</p>

							</div>

								
					
