<p>Good lord. You make me feel like an awful person (along with the rest of the human race, I'm guessing) for assuming such awful things about 231&#8230; like Clef said, our imaginations can extrapolate awful things from information only <em>implied.</em> Take your upvote and go win a Nobel Peace Prize, dammit.</p>
