			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2130362">
									

<ol>
<li>How has the King never looked in specifically to see how horrible she has it? I can't buy someone who is more or less the Sauron of the Skip'verse /not/ actually checking in and just taking a bunch of mortal emotions and reactions at face value, much less not be able to feel the girl's own emotions to see that she's not actually living a real life nightmare.</li>
<li>Nor can I understand how they keep up this charade on a cosmic and spiritual level when nobody in the observation room, nor the little girl, nor the -D even make a play at causing harm, feeling revulsion, or any other negative emotion. If he can feel the emotions of the people who read the documents, he can sure as hell feel the emotions of everyone involved in the procedures and know that they're bullshitting him.</li>
</ol>

