														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2130400">
									

<p>Hot damn, the buildup in this Tale is fucking incredible. As the events led up to Montauk actually being executed I could just feel my stomach tying itself into knots and the hairs on my neck standing upright in horror and revulsion, and that feeling of utter bewilderment and indescribable <em>relief</em> when the true nature of the procedure was revealed was fucking phenomenal. I adore how the Foundation is being both pragmatic and humane in their approach-two traits which nowadays are pretty much mutually exclusive-and the explanation for why the Foundation adopted this method makes complete sense both in and out of universe. Bra-fucking-vo, kaktus. You just won the site.</p>

							</div>

										<div class="signature">
					<hr class="signature-separator"/>
					

<p>And if the whole world is crashing down&#8230; fall through space out of mind with me.</p>

